		<title>2025 CIA500世界華人保險500強團隊領導人峰會曼谷隆重舉辦 聚焦扎根扎深與永續領導力</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/14/2025-cia500%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e8%8f%af%e4%ba%ba%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%aa500%e5%bc%b7%e5%9c%98%e9%9a%8a%e9%a0%98%e5%b0%8e%e4%ba%ba%e5%b3%b0%e6%9c%83%e6%9b%bc%e8%b0%b7%e9%9a%86%e9%87%8d%e8%88%89%e8%be%a6/</link>
		
