					<description><![CDATA[<p>記者 洪俊維 / 報導 由 SheenaGames 開發的成人修仙放置 MMORPG《紅塵問仙》於今（12）日 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/12/%e3%80%8a%e7%b4%85%e5%a1%b5%e5%95%8f%e4%bb%99%e3%80%8bx-%e3%80%8a%e8%b5%a4%e9%ac%bc%e3%80%8b-%e8%81%af%e5%8b%95%e4%bc%81%e5%8a%83%ef%bc%81%e8%b5%a4%e9%ac%bc%e6%9c%ac%e4%ba%ba%e9%85%8d%e9%9f%b3/">《紅塵問仙》× 《赤鬼》 聯動企劃！赤鬼本人配音角色登場！</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>記者 洪俊維 / 報導</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p><strong>由 SheenaGames 開發的成人修仙放置 MMORPG《紅塵問仙》於今（12）日宣佈，由於 SWAG 特別企劃反應熱烈，將加碼與知名創作者 赤鬼伯伯 展開全新聯動活動。</strong></p>
</blockquote>



<p>本次推出限定聯動角色「<strong>赤鬼伯伯</strong>」，並開放兩套限定時裝，玩家入手後將能解鎖「赤鬼」本人親自配音的福利劇情。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1220" height="686" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%80_1920x1080.jpg?resize=1220%2C686&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-280528" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%80_1920x1080.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%80_1920x1080.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%80_1920x1080.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%80_1920x1080.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" /></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>赤鬼降臨紅塵：鏡中異界的修仙奇緣</strong><strong></strong></h2>



<p>知名創作者「赤鬼伯伯」在直播中介紹一面神秘古鏡，卻在鏡光閃爍之際被吞入異界，靈魂降臨九州修仙大陸！你在山林間發現這位滿口怪話、舉止詭異的女子，將她帶回宗門，卻意外捲入一場跨界的奇異事件。道天宗長老璇璣透露，這面古鏡似乎是通往他界的入口，過去也曾有人因此失蹤。為了揭開鏡中之謎，你與赤鬼伯伯踏上調查之路，與鏡花、水月等人同行，深入山林與幽湖之底，對抗潛伏的妖獸與巨影。隨著真相逐漸浮現，鏡中的世界與紅塵界之間的界線也愈發模糊。這場命定的相遇，究竟是意外，還是一場早已注定的緣？</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1220" height="686" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%BA%8C_1920x1080.jpg?resize=1220%2C686&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-280529" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%BA%8C_1920x1080.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%BA%8C_1920x1080.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%BA%8C_1920x1080.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%BA%8C_1920x1080.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" /></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>色狗們集合！赤鬼專屬福利來啦！</strong></h2>



<p>本次與<strong>赤鬼伯伯</strong>的真人聯動，帶來香氣撲鼻的專屬福利劇情，為玩家打造幸福體驗。</p>



<p>玩家只要取得「華服與贈禮」或「異世界修真者」其中一套限定時裝，並取得「赤鬼」的好感提升羈絆度，就能與色氣滿滿的赤鬼雙修。赤鬼的色狗們還在等甚麼立即登入《紅塵問仙》，與赤鬼共修紅塵之路！</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1220" height="686" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%89_1920x1080.jpg?resize=1220%2C686&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-280531" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%89_1920x1080.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%89_1920x1080.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%89_1920x1080.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/%E5%9C%96%E4%B8%89_1920x1080.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" /></figure>



