										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>記者 陳聖偉 / 報導</p>



<p>萬眾期待的國際電競盛會「2025臺北城市盃國際電競大賽」於11月8日、9日在捷運展演廳完美落幕！為期兩天的賽事共吸引超過千名觀眾到場同樂，本屆賽事為呼應明年度的名古屋亞運電競項目，選定《快打旋風6》與《傳說對決》為主題比賽，現場熱情高漲、掌聲不斷。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="866" height="487" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-103.png?resize=866%2C487&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-281005" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-103.png?w=866&amp;ssl=1 866w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-103.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-103.png?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 866px) 100vw, 866px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">由左至右為ETToday東森新媒體控股顧睿誠副總經理、威剛科技邱雅筑經理、魔杰股份有限公司邱冠鴻總監、臺北市政府體育局游竹萍局長、台全醫療體系林明杰執行長、共享數位服務姜建丞董事</figcaption></figure>



<p> 《快打旋風6》最終決賽中，香港隊（Hotdog29、Scarlet_pc） 以絕佳操作與穩定節奏擊敗新加坡隊（Xian、cola321），其中Scarlet_pc同時也是臺北熊讚隊的年輕選手，透過賽前分組，與熱狗選手摘下本屆冠軍榮耀。而《傳說對決》公開賽，冠軍由臺北市在地學校稻江商職「稻江哈士奇」勇奪，最後一局在一勝一負的情況下，最終逆轉拿下傳說對決冠軍，亞軍為萬能科大「萬能雄獅VNU」，季軍與殿軍由黎明技術學院「黎明企鵝」與莊敬高職「JJVS」奪得。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="873" height="582" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-104.png?resize=873%2C582&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-281009" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-104.png?w=873&amp;ssl=1 873w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-104.png?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 873px) 100vw, 873px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="873" height="492" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-105.png?resize=873%2C492&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-281010" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-105.png?w=873&amp;ssl=1 873w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-105.png?resize=768%2C433&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-105.png?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 873px) 100vw, 873px" /></figure>



<p>除了激烈賽事外，更邀請多組人氣嘉賓登台助陣，AcQUA源少年帶來青春舞曲開場搭配現場粉絲大力應援、Fubon Angels啦啦隊用熱情舞蹈炒熱氣氛同時與現場民眾同樂競技、木莓FRUCTOSE帶來甜系舞台演出，讓觀眾在電競與音樂間盡情沉浸。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="866" height="487" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-106.png?resize=866%2C487&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-281011" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-106.png?w=866&amp;ssl=1 866w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-106.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-106.png?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 866px) 100vw, 866px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">(AcQUA源少年表演照)</figcaption></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="866" height="487" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-107.png?resize=866%2C487&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-281012" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-107.png?w=866&amp;ssl=1 866w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-107.png?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-107.png?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 866px) 100vw, 866px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">(Fubon Angels啦啦隊)</figcaption></figure>



<p>活動會場同時設有AI科技體驗區、電競週邊展示、抽獎活動等多元互動攤位，觀眾不僅能近距離欣賞高水準比賽，更能參與活動、帶走限量好禮，並透過攤位交流，了解電子競技更多的衍伸性。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="864" height="576" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-108.png?resize=864%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-281013" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-108.png?w=864&amp;ssl=1 864w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image-108.png?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px" /></figure>



<p>「臺北城市盃國際電競大賽」已成為年度指標性國際賽事，「魔杰股份有限公司」行銷總監邱冠鴻表示:透過跨國邀請知名選手來臺灣參與賽事，除了使民眾更瞭解電子競技的魅力外，也能讓臺灣年輕選手有機會汲取國際職業選手的經驗，進而培育更多台北市的潛力選手。更希望透過這個電競賽事IP，讓臺北市成為青年文化、數位娛樂、音樂展演的交流平台，讓更多人看見臺北的美好。</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/12/%e3%80%8c2025%e8%87%ba%e5%8c%97%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82%e7%9b%83%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e9%9b%bb%e7%ab%b6%e5%a4%a7%e8%b3%bd%e3%80%8d%e7%86%b1%e8%a1%80%e8%90%bd%e5%b9%95%ef%bc%81%e5%9b%9b%e5%9f%8e%e9%81%b8/">「2025臺北城市盃國際電競大賽」熱血落幕！四城選手巔峰對決、校園新星閃耀全場！</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
